title: Players hurt by free agency
itunes:title: Players hurt by free agency
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler react to the latest news in the NFL, including the New England Patriots trading defensive end Chandler Jones to the Arizona Cardinals. Then, the heroes dive into another speed round before ending the show breaking down players who have been hurt by free agency.
